// overview main text. num switch is an app to be used in conjunction with the num range of accessories/moduals. \nThe num app uses bluetooth technology to communicate with the num range of accessories. \nPlease read the setup for information on the set up procedure.
// setup main text 1. Assign your num modual outputs with a different number and make a note of the relevant bluetooth ID for each output. \n2. connect the moduals to a 5v-9V DC power supply.\n3. Load up your num switch app and click on the bluetooth Sync button on the home screen. \n4. Enter the bluetooth ID number supplied with each modual in the relevant bluetooth ID field. \n5. Then press the Sync button. \n6. Now when you pick a num from the home screen you can turn on/off the relevant output number.
